sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant PSC as processSlashCommand
    participant Cmd as clear 命令
    participant REPL as REPL 层

    User->>PSC: 输入 "/clear"
    PSC->>PSC: findCommand("clear", commands)
    PSC->>Cmd: cmd.load() → import('./clear.js')
    Cmd->>Cmd: clearConversation(context)
    Cmd-->>PSC: { type: 'text', value: '' }
    PSC-->>REPL: SystemLocalCommandMessage
    Note over REPL: 本地消费，不触发 LLM
